1
00:01:13,847 --> 00:01:15,017
You're causing chaos

2
00:01:15,017 --> 00:01:16,346
across the land at any cost,

3
00:01:16,467 --> 00:01:17,887
just for the sake of one man?

4
00:01:18,007 --> 00:01:19,096
I'll guard the country,

5
00:01:19,677 --> 00:01:21,637
and I'll have the man too

6
00:01:31,637 --> 00:01:32,467
Finished?

7
00:01:32,677 --> 00:01:33,427
Caught?

8
00:01:33,887 --> 00:01:34,887
Just like that?

9
00:01:50,387 --> 00:01:53,927
May Your Majesty live and reign for ten thousand years, ten thousand of ten thousand years!

10
00:01:55,307 --> 00:01:56,517
All the ministers, please rise

11
00:01:57,137 --> 00:01:58,717
Thank you, Your Majesty

12
00:02:29,887 --> 00:02:33,137
You can't drive me away, idiot

13
00:02:34,467 --> 00:02:35,677
Finally, the two little caterpillars of the Northern Kingdom

14
00:02:35,677 --> 00:02:37,267
was sent away

15
00:02:37,887 --> 00:02:38,767
This time, Chen

16
00:02:38,767 --> 00:02:40,217
is definitely getting Her Majesty's favor

17
00:02:40,677 --> 00:02:41,557
Then,

18
00:02:41,557 --> 00:02:42,926
don't forget us

19
00:02:44,467 --> 00:02:46,677
Besides, Chen and Her Majesty are in true love

20
00:02:46,677 --> 00:02:48,347
That's a friendship forged through life and death

21
00:02:48,887 --> 00:02:51,097
Slap the mouth. It's love through life and death

22
00:02:51,097 --> 00:02:53,307
Love through life and death. Your Majesty

23
00:02:54,057 --> 00:02:54,926
Don't be the third wheel

24
00:02:57,887 --> 00:02:59,057
Your Majesty, how come you are free today

25
00:02:59,057 --> 00:03:00,136
to come to our Cold Palace?

26
00:03:01,927 --> 00:03:03,057
Rebellion is disbanded

27
00:03:03,137 --> 00:03:04,097
The court is stable now

28
00:03:04,557 --> 00:03:06,307
You don't have to idle your life in the palace anymore

29
00:03:08,467 --> 00:03:09,267
Leave here

30
00:03:09,677 --> 00:03:10,637
I want to marry you

31
00:03:12,267 --> 00:03:12,967
But

32
00:03:21,767 --> 00:03:24,767
Even if it means dying for you across lifetimes,

33
00:03:25,557 --> 00:03:27,136
I'll be with you

34
00:03:59,677 --> 00:04:00,467
Ye Nanchen

35
00:04:07,427 --> 00:04:08,347
Next time,

36
00:04:09,467 --> 00:04:11,007
I'll buy you a new doll

37
00:05:02,387 --> 00:05:03,177
Hong Dou

38
00:05:04,137 --> 00:05:05,097
I like you

39
00:05:06,217 --> 00:05:07,927
Would you like to stay with me forever?

40
00:05:23,057 --> 00:05:24,596
Don't push me away anymore

41
00:05:36,847 --> 00:05:38,097
Even if it means dying for you

42
00:05:38,557 --> 00:05:39,807
across lifetimes,

43
00:05:41,057 --> 00:05:42,346
I'll be with you

44
00:06:06,427 --> 00:06:08,887
If we share the snow today,

45
00:06:11,307 --> 00:06:14,767
this will be counted as getting our hair gray together

46
00:06:34,217 --> 00:06:35,597
Happy wrap-up!

47
00:06:39,717 --> 00:06:41,097
Happy wrap-up!

48
00:06:47,387 --> 00:06:49,637
Happy wrap-up!
